<h3><span>与腾讯财经联合推出</span><a href="http://special.caixin.com/interview/">精英访谈</a></h3>
<dl>
<dt>
<div class=pic><a href="http://special.caixin.com/2014-01-29/100635329.html"><img src="http://img.caixin.com/2013-12-11/1386728806280933.jpg"></a></div>
